{"_path":"/maps/_person/technology/steve-blank","_dir":"technology","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Steve Blank","description":"硅谷创业教父、精益创业运动发起人，《四步创业法》作者","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Steve Blank 是硅谷最具影响力的创业思想家之一，精益创业（Lean Startup）运动的发起人。\n他曾是八家科技公司的创始人，后转向教学，在斯坦福大学、加州大学伯克利分校等高校讲授创业课程。\n其著作《四步创业法》（The Four Steps to the Epiphany）被视为硅谷创业圣经，影响了 Eric Ries 等人。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"核心思想"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心思想？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"精益创业方法论"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提出\"客户开发\"（Customer Development）流程，强调在开发产品前先验证客户需求"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主张创业是\"可管理的、可重复的过程\"，而非依赖天才的随机行为"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"推动\"最小可行产品\"（MVP）和快速迭代理念在创业界的普及"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"洞见与思考"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"洞见与思考？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"关系结束是一种\"人生转向\""}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Steve Blank 认为，关系的结束不应被视为失败，而是一种正常的\"人生转向\"（life pivot）。\n他通过亲身经历说明：长期关系往往会进入\"自动运行\"状态，直到某个\"警醒时刻\"（wake-up call）迫使你重新评估。\n人、机构、目标都会随时间变化，关系的结束通常意味着成长发生，而非失败。\n他提出七种关系结束的信号：关系为\"过去的你/对方\"而建、共同使命到期、隐性契约改变、长期不一致、留下的成本上升等。\n这种思维框架不仅适用于人际关系，也适用于创业伙伴关系、组织支持决策等场景。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://steveblank.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Steve Blank 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://steveblank.com/2026/02/24/time-to-move-on-the-reason-relationships-end/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Time to Move On – The Reason Relationships End"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_person:technology:steve-blank.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_person/technology/steve-blank.md","_stem":"6.maps/_person/technology/steve-blank","_extension":"md"}